### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Registro (primera vez con este email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Registro duplicado (mismo email — debe fallar con 400/422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Login — credenciales inválidas (ajustá el password si querés probar 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "password-incorrecto"
}

### Me — sesión actual (401 si @accessToken vacío o expirado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Me — sin token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

### Validación — falta email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Balance smart wallet (mock chain; JWT obligatorio)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/wallet/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Balance caja fuerte (mock; requiere fila caja_fuerte en DB)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/caja-fuerte/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

